 Chun / Los Angeles Times通过Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-joni-mitchell-perform-both-sides-now-at-la-fireaid-benefit-gig-3833579">乔尼·米切尔（Joni Mitchell）在LA FireeAid福利展上表现出色</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>则联手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-join-green-day-for-last-night-on-earth-at-la-fireaid-concert-3833458">为“昨晚在地球上”进行了现场演绎</a>，毫无疑问， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-no-doubt-reunite-for-medley-of-hits-at-la-fireaid-concert-3833481">毫无疑问地参加了他们的一些热门歌曲</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-surviving-members-of-nirvana-reunite-with-joan-jett-kim-gordon-and-st-vincent-at-la-fires-benefit-concert-3833434">Nirvana幸存的成员也出人意料的是</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">圣文森特</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-gordon">金·</a>戈登（Kim Gordon），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joan-jett">琼·杰特（Joan Jett）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">戴夫·格罗尔（Dave Grohl）</a>的女儿紫罗兰（Violet）在人声中加入。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-debut-la-wildfires-inspired-new-song-all-i-need-is-time-at-fireaid-3833774">Lady Gaga还分享了一首新歌，直接受到FireAid野火的启发</a>，标题为“我需要的是时间”。同样，许多音乐家加紧帮助受影响的社区，在大火之后。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-foundation-announces-2-5million-donation-to-la-wildfire-relief-3828303">碧昂斯的Beygood基金会捐赠了250万美元，</a>以帮助救济工作。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-launches-fund-for-families-displaced-by-the-la-wildfires-3828081">巴黎·希尔顿（Paris Hilton）还为被大火流离失所的家庭开设了一项基金</a>，承诺要捐款100,000美元，最高可达100,000美元的捐款。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-spent-birthday-making-meals-for-families-hit-by-la-wildfires-3829226">戴夫·格罗尔（Dave Grohl）还为受影响的家庭度过了生日</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-justin-bieber-steve-carell-and-more-set-to-appear-in-charity-hockey-event-