://www.nme.com/artists/the-japanese-house">日本房屋</a>）在内的合着者和制片人制作的。</p><h2> <strong>“牡蛎”曲目列表：</strong> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;抓住&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;生的&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“讨厌它”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;深渊&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;牡蛎&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“海岸线”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“寄生虫”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;7海</strong></li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;虚弱的&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;使用&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-def